{
  "stem": "11744.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the-- my husband said that a lot of people joined the last 15 minutes of the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, then we had a-- a big resisting-- Even our president, Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mitterrand first worked for Vichy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When he came back from the prisoner of war camp, he did the same thing my husband did-- he also walked back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he went to Vichy and worked for Petain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, in 1943, he joined the Resistance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was very late in the game.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So many.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, my husband especially because he had groups form that were much bigger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to form new groups, i mean, and to then-- to then-- and find new places to hide them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How often he was coming?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, not very often.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The last time I saw him was the 25th of May 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The day of his 35th birthday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the last time I met him, I met him in in Lyon-- in the big city of Lyon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And spent-- we had dinner together, spent the night there, he left the next morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I left to go back where I lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was killed exactly a month later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This friend of mine-- this friend of mine that I mentioned when I said he was the one who was playing double games, and making those ID cards, and all of that-- and he was little man who looked like nothing.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, my-- my second husband met him when I took him to France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was absolutely flabbergasted to see a little man like this, with absolutely no-- no prestige, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How could he have done so much in the underground?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
